<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Flight Ticket Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      background-color: #0073e6;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .details {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-left: 4px solid #0073e6;
    }
    .details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .social-icons {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .social-icons a {
      margin: 0 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #0073e6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Your Flight Ticket Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Dear {{name}},</h2>
      <p>We are pleased to confirm your flight booking. Please find your e-ticket attached to this email. Kindly review the details carefully to ensure all information is correct.</p>
      <div class="details">
        <p><strong>Booking Details:</strong></p>
        <p>Passenger Name: {{name}}</p>
        <p>Booking ID: {{bookingReference}}</p>
        <p>Flight Number: {{flightNumber}}</p>
        <p>Date of Travel: {{travelDate}}</p>
        <p>Departure Time: {{departureTime}}</p>
        <p>Arrival Time: {{arrivalTime}}</p>
        <p>PNR/Booking Reference: {{pnr}}</p>
      </div>
      <p>Please ensure to carry a valid ID along with this ticket during your travel. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing {{companyName}}!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <h2><strong>{{companyName}}</strong></h2>
      <p>üìû {{phoneNumber}} | üìß {{emailAddress}}</p>
      <p>üåê {{websiteUrl}}</p>
      <p>üè¢ {{companyAddress}}</p>
      <div class="social-icons">
        Follow us on:
        <a href="{{facebookUrl}}">Facebook</a>
        <a href="{{instagramUrl}}">Instagram</a>
        <a href="{{twitterUrl}}">Twitter</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
